<HEADLINE>
<P>
NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Tickets for UC Irvine-sponsored events at the Irvine Barclay Theatre are on 
sale now even though the theater is still under construction and will not open 
until October. 
</P>
<P>
More than 60 events, including an Opera a la Carte production of Gilbert and 
Sullivan's "H.M.S. Pinafore" and the Royal New Zealand Ballet's "Coppelia," 
have been scheluded at the 750-seat theater. Tickets will range from $12 to 
$30. For information, call the Arts and Lectures office at UC Irvine, (714) 
856-6379. 
</P>
</TEXT>
