<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Barry Bonds and R.J. Reynolds, fined $1,500 apiece for missing the Pittsburgh 
Pirates' team-sponsored charity auction, plan to appeal. 
</P>
<P>
Fans attending paid an admission fee plus an additional charge depending on the 
