<P>
REGIONAL EARNINGS: PERFECTDATA POSTS STRONGEST 1ST QUARTER IN ITS HISTORY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PerfectData Corp., a Simi Valley maker of cleaning and maintenance supplies for 
computer equipment, reported a $138,000 profit in its fiscal first-quarter that 
ended June 30. 
</P>
<P>
A year earlier, the company earned less than $1,000 in the quarter. 
</P>
<P>
The higher profit came on an 84% jump in PerfectData's sales, to $1.42 million 
from $773,000. The company attributed the gains to recent restructuring efforts 
and said it was the strongest fiscal first quarter in its history. 
