<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGIONAL PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TransWorld Bank in Sherman Oaks promoted Diane Auten to vice president and 
manager of its central note department. She previously was an assistant vice 
president. 
</P>
<P>
The department supports loan-document processing, wire transfers, certificates 
of deposit and individual retirement accounts. 
</P>
</TEXT>
