<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Japanese car ; Chart, EUROPEAN COMMUNITY'S NEW PASSENGER CAR 
REGISTRATIONS, Los Angeles Times ; Chart, PRIVATE CARS AND LIGHT COMMERCIAL 
VEHICLE IMPORTS 1988, Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
NISSAN MOTOR CORP; AUTOMOBILE INDUSTRY -- ENGLAND; AUTOMOBILE INDUSTRY -- 
EUROPE; JAPAN -- TRADE -- EUROPE; JOINT VENTURES; FOREIGN OWNED CORPORATIONS; 
EUROPEAN UNIFICATION; EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES 
</P>
