<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Fatal fight -- An article Sunday incorrectly reported that a Van Nuys man died 
as a result of injuries he received during a fight in FM Station, a nightclub 
in North Hollywood. In fact, the victim, Leo Firpo, was attacked in a parking 
lot outside the bar, police said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
</TYPE>
